==Applications== All of the applications are free except for Counter-Strike: Source. Let's take a look at the applications that you will be using:
{| border="1" cellpadding="0" style="background-color:#F8FBFF;text-align:left" |- !Application!!Use!!Comes with Source SDK |- |Steam||platform required for Source SDK to function||&nbsp; |- |Counter-Strike: Source||testing the actual look of your model in the game||yes |- |Source SDK||provides a source of tools for compiling models||&nbsp; |- |[http://chaosincarnate.net/cannonfodder/mdldecompiler.php Cannonfodder's mdl decompiler]||decompiles original models as a guideline to compiling a new model||yes |- |studiomdl||compiling models||yes |- |HLMV (Half Life Model Viewer)||preview compiled models||yes |- |vtex||Convert TGA textures to VTF textures||yes |- |[http://www.irfanview.com/main_download_engl.htm IrfanView]||converting the textures to BMP format||no |- |[http://nemesis.thewavelength.net/index.php?p=26 GCFScape]||extracting the original files out of the game||no |- |[http://www.softimage.com/downloads/XSI_Mod_Tool/default.aspx SOFTIMAGE®<nowiki>|</nowiki>XSI® 6 Mod Tool] (with ValveSource addon)||animating the model and exporting it||no |- |[http://www.softimage.com/downloads/XSI_Patch/default.aspx XSI Mod Tool 6 Update]||updating XSI Mod Tool to a more stable version||no |- |[http://www.softimage.com/downloads/crosswalk/default.aspx Crosswalk]||merging XSI Mod Tool 6 scenes||no |- |[http://download.cnet.com/Softimage-XSI-Mod-Tool/3000-18541_4-10343972.html SOFTIMAGE®<nowiki>|</nowiki>XSI® 4.2 Mod Tool] (with [http://www.fileplanet.com/148788/140000/fileinfo/ ValveSource] addon)||rigging the model and merging it||no |- |Text editor||editing the QC file||no |}
==Why do you need 2 XSI Mod Tools?== You need two XSI Mod Tools because XSI Mod Tool 6 is not fully functional for our purposes. Mod Tool 6 cannot merge scenes or import smds properly. Here is a feature comparison of the two Mod Tools. {| border="1" cellpadding="0" style="background-color:#F8FBFF;text-align:left" |- !Feature!!XSI Mod Tool 6!!XSI Mod Tool 4.2 |- |import smds with proper skeletons||No||Yes |- |export smds with proper skeletons||Yes||yes, sometimes doesn't work |- |Merge Scenes||yes||yes (easier) |- |open Mod Tool 4.2 scenes||yes||yes |- |open Mod Tool 6 scenes||yes||no |- |registration required to save and export scenes||no||yes |}
Click [http://www.softimage.com/products/modtool/activate/default.asp?bhcp=1 here] to register XSI Mod Tool 4.2.
