== How long have you been working for? ==
How would you respond to: (Assume for these questions that your name is Zipho Mtembu and that you're a student in Cape Town in your 3rd year. But you come from Johannesburg. You are 23 years old. Your brother works at Crispy Chicken as a cook. Your mother is a nurse. Your sister is teacher.)
{{Question-answer
| question = Uneminyaka emingaki usebenza?
| answer = Cha, ngiyafunda.
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = Uneminyaka emingaki ufunda?
| answer = Ngineminyaka eng-3 ngifunda.
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = Wena uphumaphi?
| answer = (Mina) ngiphuma eGoli.
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = Isibongo satho ngubani?
| answer = Isibango sami uMtembu
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = Ngihlala kuphi?
| answer = Sawubona mntwana!
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = Ungubani?
| answer = NginguZipho.
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = Wena unjani?
| answer = Ngikhona/ ngisaphila/ ngiyaphila.
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = Ubhuti wakho usebenzaphi?
| answer = Ubhuti wami/Yena usebenza eCrispy Chicken.
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = Uneminyaka emingaki ubudala?
| answer = Ngineminyaka engu-23.
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = Usisi wakho ungunesi?
| answer = Cha, usisi wami/ yena unguthisha.
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = Ubhuti wakho wenza msbenzi muni?
| answer = Ubhuti wami/ yena ungumpheki.
}}



== Age and Where do you... ==
Translate the following Zulu sentences into English:
