| question = Ngifunda eGoli.
| answer = I study in Johannesburg.
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = Wena Uneminyaka emingaki ubudala? 
| answer = How old are you/ (How many years do you have since birth)?
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = Sihlala eNaturena.
| answer = We stay in Naturena.
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = Yena usebenza kuphi?
| answer =  Where does he/she work?
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = Yena uphuma eMeliki.
| answer = He/She comes from America. 
}}
{{Question-answer
| question = Umyeni wami usebenzela iNedbank.
| answer = My husband works for Nedbank. 
}}

